data.message: Set up CI/CD for Duro adversarial tests: Created GitHub Actions workflow (adversarial-tests.yml) that runs 280 tests on Ubuntu/Windows with Python 3.11-3.13. Separates property-based tests for deterministic seeding. Commit c0bdeb5 pushed.
